title: Almighty Suspect on Fighting Nhale, Blueface Beef, Falling Out with Frosty & more
description:
Almighty Suspect clears up and debunks everything Nhale said in his interview with Adam! Nhale seems to be the one who actually started it a while back, Almighty said it would be on site, doesn't matter when. Nhale claimed he didn't know why it happened, Almighty explains everything.

-----
00:00 Intro
0:25 Almighty pays respect to Sharp: "He's one of the greats!"
1:21 Flakko thinks he's smaller than Zay, Almighty calls him delusional
2:45 Rappers bringing money to their No Jumper interviews are insecure like Nhale did after their altercation
3:30 Almighty says Nhale is lying, his manager was called for a boxing match and he never answered
5:50 Nhale said Almighty was clout chasing, Almighty says nobody knows Nhale, asks Flakko to pull out receipts
7:17 Almighty pulls out his stream numbers: "Clout chasing where!?"
11:04 Thought he might be into battle rap but ultimately, he says no one wanna hear that
12:29 Almighty on Clubhouse insinuating that Blueface paid his way to claim Schoolyard
15:23 Almighty says most rappers are winning because of everything else but music and talent
17:25 Blueface has a bigger fanbase so Almighty had been called copycat before + They used to hang out together all the time
25:00 Almighty praises Sharp and highly enjoyed the Toe Sucker interview
27:17 Almighty is the one who parted ways with Frosty coz he always felt let down by Frosty
29:24 Frosty stole Almighty's camera and pawned it
33:26 Has anybody reached out to "defend" Nate Dogg's son, like Dogg Pound? Zay asks: "Who are they?"
38:15 Almighty says it depends on the interviewer's background whether they can ask Police questions and up to the talent to say what's appropriate
38:56 Almighty reacts to Flakko and 16's interview, says he would have popped off on Flakko way earlier
39:34 Almighty says Nhale had the nerve to call him a clout chaser, Nhale is the one who started online calling him "lil boy"
41:53 "People talk crazy online thinking they can't be touched"
52:18 Nhale was embarrassed and lied about Almighty packing and wearing a ski mask
56:56 Almighty's bottom line: "Watch what you say online thinking you won't see the person you're disrespecting"
59:52 Almighty was always down to box but Nhale should be tryna fight for free after getting slapped
1:01:04 Nhale tried to embarrass Almighty first so Almighty was determined to return the favor
-----
